name: Agog 3 Ovoid Orange Green
description: @__lindaloh__ 3D ovoid sculpture. One of a collection of 20 individual sculptural pieces from my VR world "Agog", 2021. They are variously luminous, poetic, evocative, shiny, scribbly, wacky, simple, sleek, golden, wonky, compelling, weird, colourful, minimal, maximal, simple, ethereal...
